## .NET / WPF Project Gitignore

# Build outputs
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

# IDE & Editor files
.vs/
.idea/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.csproj.user
*.DotSettings
*.DotSettings.user

# NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/

# Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*

# OS & Misc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Project-specific (из вашего кода)
debug.log
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak